Hello,

Thank you for your time during the remote connection.
We resolved the communication issue between the client and the server. As you noticed the are 2 computers still without the information.
You can allow it a day to see if it updates.
If it does not you can start the log on them and see if the same error shows. If it does you can try to reinstall the client for them or we can schedule a meeting to reregister the clients.

Kind regards
